dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Washington County, WI 2021
dc_description_s: This data represents hydrography for Washington County, Wisconsin in 2021. The following features are included: 'Washington_Hydro_LINE_2021' and 'Washington_Hydro_POLY_2021'.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://maps.washcowisco.gov/portal/apps/sites/#/maps
